Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: 'Where's the beef?'
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcfm
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Mar 1984
Advertising slogan 'Where's the beef' is taken up by Democrats in the race for the presidential nomination. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less